<div id="review_16258540" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/16258540" />
    <a title="Beth" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/184038-beth"><img alt="Beth" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1220707781p2/184038.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/16258540?book_show_action=true">Feb 24, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Beth" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Beth" href="/user/show/184038-beth">Beth</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer16258540" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5835384559528587084">Comprehensively and entertainingly covers American (and some international) food history, with greatest detail focused on the last four decades. Please don&apos;t be put off by the title. David Kamp not only expertly tells a really good story, he packs in so many well-indexed details that I anticipate this book serving as a handy reference. </span>
  <span id="freeText5835384559528587084" style="display:none">Comprehensively and entertainingly covers American (and some international) food history, with greatest detail focused on the last four decades. Please don't be put off by the title. David Kamp not only expertly tells a really good story, he packs in so many well-indexed details that I anticipate this book serving as a handy reference. </span>
  <a data-text-id="5835384559528587084" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


