<span id="freeTextContainer16291904172364088378">I found this to be an engaging and entertaining look at the history of food culture, and the people who have made it, in the US. I came away knowing a little bit (and sometimes a lot) more about the people, places, and movements (or trends, if you&apos;d prefer) that have brought us to where we are today. </span>
  <span id="freeText16291904172364088378" style="display:none">I found this to be an engaging and entertaining look at the history of food culture, and the people who have made it, in the US. I came away knowing a little bit (and sometimes a lot) more about the people, places, and movements (or trends, if you'd prefer) that have brought us to where we are today. </span>
